Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:40.52,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1.5\3c&H060605&\b0\pos(356,610)}第22話  to The DarkSky -護法-
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.74,0:00:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要成為夏目的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,會永遠保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這下你就是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎君能來東京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,能跟大家在一起 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目你等著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我馬上 我馬上給你治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(640,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,急急如律令 xN
